# Generated / runtime artifacts for the csv_synchronized_windows demo.
# All regenerable — generate.py is deterministically seeded, so the
# committed source (generate.py / labchart_to_csv.py / rehearse.py /
# DEMO.md / README.md) reproduces everything below identically.

# The synthetic ten-subject cohort (~10 MB) — run generate.py.
data/

# The isolated Claude Desktop demo environment (config + runtime
# SQLite databases) — set up per README.md.
demo_env/

# A copy-paste csv_dir config block written by generate.py; carries a
# machine-specific absolute path.
user_config.sample.json
